Several allies of former President Donald Trump have shown up at the Manhattan courthouse to support him while he’s on trial.&nbsp;
Attendees at Trump’s hush-money trial have so far included the Republican House Speaker, several members of Congress, state attorneys general, and two of Trump’s former presidential primary opponents. Notably absent is Melania Trump, the former First Lady, who is yet to appear in the courthouse.
The politicians rallying behind Trump used their presence at the courtroom to attack witness testimony, since the former President is barred from publicly commenting on key figures in the trial.

